Moyal  from Witten's  for fermionic modes 
 

The second step in constructing the map from Witten's star to Moyal's star
is to perform the Fourier transformation from position space to momentum
space for a subset of string modes. We recall the definition of
Witten's -product for functions of split strings in the ghost sector 
 
